#CHIP YM3812
#CLOCK 3579545

; OPL2 (YM3812) Basic FM Test — 2-operator synthesis
;
; The YM3812 OPL2 chip has 9 channels, each supporting 2-operator FM synthesis.
; This test validates basic 2-operator patch generation.
;
; Tests:
; - All 9 channels with independent melodies
; - 2-operator FM timbre
; - Envelope control
; - Register accuracy

#TRACK 0

TEMPO 120

; Channel 1-3: Melody
c4 . d4 . e4 .

r4

; Channel 4-6: Harmony (thirds)
e4 . f4 . g4 .

r4

; Channel 7-9: Bass line
c3 . . d3 . . e3 .

r4

; All 9 channels together (brief)
c4 & e4 & c3 .

r2

#END
